title: [Haunted Pass, Dense Trees]
description: The path is choked with vegetation, offering little scenery other than the greenness surrounding the area.  A rotting tree trunk lies on its side just to the west and is covered in all sorts of fungi.  Through the foliage, a phantasmal grove of trees clumps together deep in the woods.
